Leadership


    The Vocera leadership team  
 

The Vocera leadership team has developed a culture of innovation with a focus on delivering value and service to its customers. The team includes information technology, healthcare and mobility industry executives with operational experience and understanding of U.S. and international mission-critical industries the company’s solutions and services address.







