Vocera Badge 


    Hands-Free, Wearable, Lightweight, and Voice-Controlled   


 Say goodbye to overhead paging and long call-and-wait cycles. Say hello to the Vocera Badge.
The Badge is much more than a communication device; it’s your small and mighty gateway to the leading platform for clinical communication and workflow.
That’s right: only the Vocera Platform lets you integrate with more than 120 clinical and operational systems to get the information you need – no more, no less – when and where you need it.
And only the Vocera Badge lets you do it all, hands-free.
If you want to talk to somebody, just tap your Badge and find them (intelligent call routing makes it easy), and have your conversation. Use your Badge hands-free to stay at a patient’s bedside while communicating. Hold it like a handset for more privacy. 




